de.braintags.io.vertx.pojomapper.init

Class DataStoreSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.braintags.io.vertx.pojomapper.init.DataStoreSettings

  • public class DataStoreSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    Preferences to initialize an IDataStore By using this defintion you are able to instantiate an instance of IDataStoreInit defined by getDatastoreInit() and instantiate an IDataStore by using the Properties inside the current class
